                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18220220-115-victim1140 t18220220-115-viclabel625"></join>, and live in Oxford-street. On the 16th of February, about quarter before seven o'clock, I was going up Oxford-street, and crossing the <placeName id="t18220220-115-crimeloc626">Regent's Circus</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18220220-115-crimeloc626" type="placeName" value="Regent's Circus"></interp>
