                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18220220-115-off623 t18220220-115-crimeloc626"></join>, I felt my handkerchief going from my pocket, turned round, and saw the prisoner wrapping something in his apron. I took hold of him, and found my handkerchief in his apron. He said he had not got it.</p>
